    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Of course it is possible :)</p>\n\n<pre><code>String newStr = str.replaceAll(\",\",\"\");\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>For removing even spaces :</p>\n\n<pre><code>String newStr = str.replaceAll(\",\",\"\").replaceAll(\" \",\"\");\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>And you can pass it to Long immediately</p>\n\n<pre><code>Long myLong = Long.valueOf(str.replaceAll(\",\",\"\").replaceAll(\" \",\"\"));\n</code></pre>\n"
